---
title: Fast Leveling
hidden: false
---
**Fast leveling** allows the player to level up much quicker than usual. While the game normally provides acceleration when holding the level-up arrow, this method triggers that maximum speed right from the start. You can achieve this using specific keybinds, as explained in the video below.

